15
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,790
I am poor,

16
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,440
but I would never steal.

17
00:01:53,690 --> 00:01:56,480
I just wanted to try it on.

18
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:58,830
All right, Mama Jinzhi.

19
00:01:58,830 --> 00:01:59,720
Don’t be angry.

20
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,310
It’s gone now.

21
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,080
Qianyu,

22
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,720
I’m sorry.

23
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,830
I put you in that awkward position.

24
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:19,470
Mom, you didn’t.

25
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,160
You think too much.

26
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,320
Let’s go home.

27
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:26,460
Let’s go.

28
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,200
That’s it.

29
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,000
I think it’s OK.

30
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:56,030
The goddamned bracelet

31
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:58,000
was stuck on my wrist for all day!

32
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,670
I’m relieved, finally.

33
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:04,190
All right.

34
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:06,520
It’ll be over after we send it back tomorrow.

35
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,440
I’m sorry you have to go back there.

36
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,190
Mom, it’s OK.

37
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:32,440
Is Qianyu alright?

38
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,960
Jinzhi.

39
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,440
I…

40
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:41,520
I’ll work hard on the inn

41
00:03:42,270 --> 00:03:44,920
and give you a better life.

42
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,190
Why do you bring it up?

43
00:03:51,550 --> 00:03:53,190
I’ll go check on Qianyu.

44
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:54,190
Sure.

45
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:02,160
Mom, you must be tired.

46
00:04:02,550 --> 00:04:03,800
I’ve never met

47
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,880
such an outrageous family.

48
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,160
Junhao,

49
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:15,240
fire Ye Qianyu immediately.

50
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:17,230
Mom,

51
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:21,000
Ye Qianyu didn’t do anything wrong.

52
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,950
Senwell won’t

53
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,510
fire an employee without good reason.

54
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:28,480
As one of the service staff of Senwell Hotel

55
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,720
and a waitress of the party,

56
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,790
she connived at her mom’s thievery.

57
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,040
Isn’t that wrong?

58
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,270
Ye Qianyu’s mom didn’t steal anything.

59
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,920
I’ve made it clear.

60
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,880
If Yunyi and I didn’t catch her red-handed,

61
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,390
the bracelet would have been stolen by her.

62
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,000
Doesn’t that make her a thief?

63
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,790
And she made these excuses.

64
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,920
Why did you speak for her?

65
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,480
I didn’t speak for them.

66
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,880
I just didn’t want to carry the matter further

67
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,160
on your birthday party.

68
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,000
Really?

69
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,600
Is it really for my consideration?

70
00:05:00,350 --> 00:05:01,110
OK.

71
00:05:01,550 --> 00:05:03,070
Fire Ye Qianyu immediately.

72
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,270
Mom,

73
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,160
Qianyu is a kind girl.

74
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:13,200
You shouldn’t be prejudiced against her.

75
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,200
Junhao,

76
00:05:14,550 --> 00:05:17,040
you’re about to marry Yunyi.

77
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,760
Don’t get another involved.

78
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,230
Fire Ye Qianyu immediately.

79
00:05:20,230 --> 00:05:22,760
And bring your life back to normal.

80
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:25,230
So you can be happy with Yunyi.

81
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,270
You can’t ruin

82
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,000
someone’s future with just words.

83
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:32,640
We have no right to dominate other’s life.

84
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,230
What has

85
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:43,320
that girl done to you?

86
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:45,230
Why are you defending her?

87
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:46,920
She has nothing to do with this, Mom.

88
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,070
Junhao.

89
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:49,110
Junhao,

90
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:51,200
it’s Mom’s birthday.

91
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,830
Don’t make her angry.

92
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,320
Anyway,

93
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,320
it’s gone.

94
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,510
Go to bed.

95
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,480
I have work to do.

96
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,200
What’s in your mind?

97
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,070
I’m thinking

98
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:26,480
we are not equal, actually,

99
00:06:26,670 --> 00:06:27,670
right?

100
00:06:28,550 --> 00:06:30,270
A family like ours

101
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:33,000
would surely be regarded as thieves.

102
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:38,000
In fact, in front of death and diseases,

103
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,320
we’re all equal.

104
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,390
No one can escape from that.

105
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:50,880
When they accused us of thievery,

106
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:54,600
I felt I was so insignificant and humble.

107
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:57,640
It was the first time I had that feeling.

108
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:02,440
Is it because of Shan Junhao?

109
00:07:04,110 --> 00:07:05,160
No.

110
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:08,880
Shan Junhao and Tonghao

111
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,790
are different.

112
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,200
We don’t need to care about

113
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,480
others’ judgement.

114
00:07:19,790 --> 00:07:22,230
If you change yourself due to others’ judgement,

115
00:07:22,230 --> 00:07:23,880
you’ll no longer be yourself.

116
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,790
Do you know why I like travelling?

117
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:36,550
Because when you’re on the road,

118
00:07:36,670 --> 00:07:38,230
there’s no restraints.

119
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:40,270
You can be yourself.

120
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,670
I wish I can be as free as you, too.

121
00:07:51,790 --> 00:07:53,270
As long as you want to,

122
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,200
you can be free, too.

123
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:20,000
Joey,

124
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,230
why did you replace that waitress

125
00:08:22,230 --> 00:08:23,960
to serve in Shan Mansion?

126
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:27,260
I got Mr. Shan’s notice out of blue

127
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:29,180
to assign Ye Qianyu to the party.

128
00:08:29,180 --> 00:08:32,410
She didn’t do anything wrong, did she?

129
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,640
No, I see.

130
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:49,220
= Yunyi =

131
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,180
= Yunyi =

132
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:55,400
Yunyi.

133
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,110
Junhao, where are you?

134
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:02,960
I want to be alone.

135
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,840
Don’t come back too late.

136
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,880
Don’t wait for me.

137
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,320
Go to sleep.

138
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,230
Tell Mom to go to bed early.

139
00:09:19,590 --> 00:09:21,150
I will wait for you.

140
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,110
Junhao,

141
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,000
I love you.

142
00:09:35,290 --> 00:09:36,570
Do you love me?

143
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:40,330
Yunyi,

144
00:09:41,370 --> 00:09:42,810
don’t think too much.

145
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,200
Go to bed.

146
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,960
Drive safe.

