= Guanmei Fishing Village Welcome You =

150
00:11:47,710 --> 00:11:48,760
Ye Qianyu.

151
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:52,710
What brings you here?

152
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:54,710
I don’t know, either.

153
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:59,400
I just drove my car here.

154
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,550
I’ve never come here before,

155
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:06,550
but it looks familiar.

156
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,550
Did Tonghao

157
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:25,280
come here with you before?

158
00:12:39,350 --> 00:12:40,670
It’s all gone.

159
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,150
By the way,

160
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:46,710
thank you for today.

161
00:12:48,470 --> 00:12:49,790
No need to thank me.

162
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,640
Since I met you,

163
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,960
I’ve been in a tangle.

164
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:56,320
I’m used to it.

165
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:02,230
But there’s never been a person like you.

166
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,280
What about me?

167
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:15,320
In the past, I thought

168
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:19,150
you were a common, plain,

169
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:21,760
rude and impolite person.

170
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,520
What

171
00:13:25,230 --> 00:13:27,670
about you that attracts me?

172
00:13:30,110 --> 00:13:31,880
Do you come all the way in midnight

173
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,670
to ridicule me?

174
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:38,230
You must be very bored, Mr. Shan.

175
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,710
But I’m thinking of you all the time.

176
00:13:46,590 --> 00:13:48,150
When you were bullied,

177
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:51,280
I beat that man up.

178
00:13:53,710 --> 00:13:55,350
You agreed to be someone’s date,

179
00:13:56,350 --> 00:13:58,660
so I asked you to serve the wine.

180
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:03,710
This is the first time in my life I learn

181
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:06,670
what jealousy and possessiveness are.

182
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,280
I wonder

183
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,110
what charm

184
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:15,150
in a person like you

185
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:17,470
that changes a man’s heart.

186
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:23,640
I hate to be influenced.

187
00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:26,960
I hate the person who has influence on me.

188
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:31,710
So I hate it that you come into my sight

189
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:33,200
and distract me.

190
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:36,230
Tell me.

191
00:14:37,130 --> 00:14:38,140
What should I do

192
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:40,270
to stop you from intervening my life?

193
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:42,460
What should I do

194
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:45,120
to stop myself from thinking about you?

195
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:54,110
The story of Tonghao and Ye Qianyu ended.

196
00:14:54,590 --> 00:14:56,910
If I disturb your life,

197
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:58,960
I apologize.

198
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,640
I’ll disappear.

199
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,550
Ye Qianyu,

200
00:15:10,230 --> 00:15:11,980
I didn’t know what love is

201
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:13,120
and what pain is until now.

202
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,000
Now I finally believe

203
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,320
everything about Tonghao you mentioned is real.

204
00:15:19,350 --> 00:15:20,520
In fact, when you put on the ring

205
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,880
and couldn’t take it off,

206
00:15:22,910 --> 00:15:24,230
it was a tip from destiny.

207
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:36,440
Ye Qianyu and Shan Junhao

208
00:15:37,230 --> 00:15:39,000
belong to two different worlds.

209
00:15:44,350 --> 00:15:45,470
I don’t care.

210
00:15:47,230 --> 00:15:48,790
Can you give me a chance?

211
00:16:07,110 --> 00:16:08,200
You know what?

212
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,960
When Tonghao left,

213
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:15,470
how I wish you could say these words.

214
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:19,670
But you didn’t.

215
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,080
And now,

216
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:26,000
we both have our own lives.

217
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,320
And I’m trying to forget you gradually.

218
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:35,520
Let’s just take our different paths.

219
00:16:36,110 --> 00:16:37,080
Isn’t that good?

220
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:40,230
No.

221
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,440
I don’t allow it.

222
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:57,000
In the banquet today,

223
00:16:58,400 --> 00:16:59,350
when my mom and I

224
00:16:59,350 --> 00:17:01,230
were watched by so many people,

225
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:05,070
I realized the gap between you and me.

226
00:17:08,430 --> 00:17:10,680
If we had to choose to stay together,

227
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:13,680
it would hurt lots of people,

228
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:14,950
including you.

229
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:18,800
So,

230
00:17:20,230 --> 00:17:22,310
I’ll take what happened today

231
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,800
never happened.

232
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:29,000
What happened is happened.

233
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,040
Why do you want to take it never happened?

234
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:35,160
The person I love is Tonghao.

235
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,590
Shan Junhao is Tonghao.

236
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,520
Don’t you ever

237
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:42,230
have the slightest feelings for Shan Junhao?

238
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,950
If you don’t,

239
00:17:49,710 --> 00:17:51,900
why are you wearing this ring

240
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:53,530
all the time?

241
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,160
I can put this ring

242
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,070
on my finger,

243
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:18,640
so can I throw it away,

244
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,230
like the memory about you.

245
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:46,110
Why did you do it?

246
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:49,400
Junhao,

247
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,520
where have you been?

248
00:19:57,190 --> 00:19:58,590
I need to talk to you.

249
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,880
It’s late.

250
00:20:03,350 --> 00:20:04,400
Let’s talk tomorrow.

251
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,110
Yunyi,

252
00:20:06,950 --> 00:20:08,470
I went to Guanmei Fishing Village.

253
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:13,590
Now,

254
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,680
you don’t even wanna lie to me?

255
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:24,800
I’m sorry, Yunyi.

256
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:26,640
In this period of time,

257
00:20:27,110 --> 00:20:27,830
my behaviors

258
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:29,560
must have caused you a lot of trouble.

259
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:32,160
It’s because

260
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:34,430
I wasn’t clear about my affection.

261
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:38,110
If it goes on like this,

262
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:42,000
I could only bring you more pain.

263
00:20:43,950 --> 00:20:44,880
I think

264
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,430
we should reconsider

265
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:50,000
the decision about our marriage.

266
00:20:53,280 --> 00:20:54,310
Junhao.

267
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,160
What did you say?

268
00:20:58,520 --> 00:20:59,680
I don’t agree.

269
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,710
Do you know what you’re doing?

270
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:05,310
Are you out of your mind?

271
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:07,520
I am not.

272
00:21:08,950 --> 00:21:11,230
I know very clearly what I’m doing.

273
00:21:12,470 --> 00:21:13,520
And clearly I know

274
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:15,070
what I want.

275
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,640
Did that girl

276
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:17,710
pester you again?

277
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:18,950
She didn’t pester me.

278
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:22,040
I’m pestering her.

279
00:21:22,430 --> 00:21:23,590
Don’t forget

280
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:25,040
that you’re the General Manager of Senwell,

281
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:26,880
the only successor of Shan family,

282
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,800
and Fan Yunyi’s fiancé.

283
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:29,520
Is that a person

284
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:31,110
in your status should say?

285
00:21:31,110 --> 00:21:31,800
Mom,

286
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:35,350
Yunyi and I grew up together.

287
00:21:35,350 --> 00:21:37,590
You believe we should get married.

