00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:38,430
But,

289
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:41,040
I realized finally

290
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:45,400
that our relationship is of families, not lovers.

291
00:21:47,710 --> 00:21:48,400
If I continue

292
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:50,070
the relationship with Yunyi,

293
00:21:50,590 --> 00:21:52,160
it’ll be so unfair for her.

294
00:21:53,190 --> 00:21:55,880
Yunyi should love and be loved.

295
00:21:56,110 --> 00:21:58,710
That’s why you should marry her.

296
00:21:59,710 --> 00:22:02,350
You should give her love and a happy life.

297
00:22:03,190 --> 00:22:05,430
She grew up in our family.

298
00:22:06,230 --> 00:22:07,800
She is the only choice for you,

299
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:09,880
and the best one.

300
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:11,230
Mom.

301
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:16,400
I can’t marry Yunyi.

302
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,230
Yunyi

303
00:22:23,830 --> 00:22:25,040
will meet a man

304
00:22:25,040 --> 00:22:27,520
who can give her love and happiness.

305
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,590
But that man

306
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:33,560
isn’t me.

307
00:22:36,590 --> 00:22:37,470
Yunyi,

308
00:22:40,430 --> 00:22:41,280
I’m sorry.

309
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:57,230
Darling.

310
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:00,470
Darling.

311
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:02,830
Mom.

312
00:23:03,350 --> 00:23:04,280
Mom.

313
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:08,470
Why?

314
00:23:10,670 --> 00:23:11,950
Why?

315
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,550
Mom.

316
00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:17,800
It’s all right.

317
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:19,710
I know.

318
00:23:20,070 --> 00:23:22,000
I… I understand.

319
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,400
Ye Qianyu,

320
00:23:53,110 --> 00:23:54,470
I won’t give you up.

321
00:23:54,740 --> 00:23:56,260
= Tonghao will take care of Ye Qianyu forever =

322
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:58,700
= Tonghao feeds Ye Qianyu =

323
00:24:06,540 --> 00:24:08,900
= Tonghao washes clothes for Ye Qianyu =

324
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,400
Why didn’t you

325
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:33,040
wake me up when you came in the morning?

326
00:24:33,950 --> 00:24:35,710
Because I wanted you to sleep a little longer.

327
00:24:37,190 --> 00:24:38,280
It’s already a great favor

328
00:24:38,280 --> 00:24:39,520
to pick me up after work.

329
00:24:39,590 --> 00:24:41,190
You really don’t have to
pick me up in the morning.

330
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:44,640
It’s a privilege for someone in bad mood.

331
00:24:46,830 --> 00:24:47,680
Qianyu,

332
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:49,280
I bought you breakfast.

333
00:24:49,470 --> 00:24:50,400
Eat it warm.

334
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:55,430
You bought so little.

335
00:24:55,430 --> 00:24:57,110
Have you ever considered my appetite?

336
00:24:58,710 --> 00:25:02,680
It’s already for two.

337
00:25:07,560 --> 00:25:10,000
Make it four next time. Thank you.

338
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:16,000
OK, I’ll get you breakfast for four.

339
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:24,160
Qianyu,

340
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,830
why don’t you wear

341
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:27,190
the necklace I gave you?

342
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,470
I threw it in the sea.

343
00:25:36,190 --> 00:25:37,040
I really did.

344
00:25:41,190 --> 00:25:42,350
You don’t regret it?

345
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:45,880
No.

346
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:45,280
Mom.

347
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:54,040
Junhao went to office in early morning.

348
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:56,000
Let’s have breakfast.

349
00:27:13,950 --> 00:27:14,920
Yunyi,

350
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:17,760
don’t think too much.

351
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:20,310
Junhao didn’t have a clear mind.

352
00:27:20,710 --> 00:27:21,920
He’ll get it through.

353
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:25,350
Since we were little,

354
00:27:26,430 --> 00:27:28,680
Junhao has been an independent person.

355
00:27:31,560 --> 00:27:33,350
I think when he said that,

356
00:27:34,830 --> 00:27:36,760
he probably made up his mind.

357
00:27:38,680 --> 00:27:40,000
Silly girl,

358
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:42,160
it’s far from a decision now.

359
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:44,680
Mom won’t allow

360
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:47,190
him to be with any other woman.

361
00:27:48,070 --> 00:27:49,310
You know Junhao

362
00:27:49,310 --> 00:27:50,800
is obedient to me.

363
00:27:51,230 --> 00:27:52,710
He won’t go against my will.

364
00:27:54,470 --> 00:27:55,590
It’s just

365
00:27:56,430 --> 00:27:58,760
you need to give him some time

366
00:27:58,950 --> 00:28:00,880
to cool down

367
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,950
and get it straight.

368
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:08,350
But I don’t know what to do

369
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:09,920
to make Junhao happy.

370
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,520
Maybe to him,

371
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,950
whatever I do is wrong.

372
00:28:22,470 --> 00:28:24,350
Don’t go to work today.

373
00:28:25,470 --> 00:28:27,000
Stay with me.

374
00:28:27,190 --> 00:28:29,920
Let’s go shopping, buy things

375
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:31,760
and go to the cinema, OK?

376
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:38,040
Mom, it’s OK.

377
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:41,430
It takes two in love,

378
00:28:42,230 --> 00:28:44,160
but one in my work.

379
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:04,110
Morning, Mr. Shan.

380
00:29:06,830 --> 00:29:07,520
Mr. Shan,

381
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:10,430
do you come to give us some instructions?

382
00:29:10,430 --> 00:29:11,040
No.

383
00:29:11,560 --> 00:29:13,230
I want to check the status of our rooms.

384
00:29:14,190 --> 00:29:15,350
Let me be your guide.

385
00:29:15,350 --> 00:29:16,190
No, thanks.

386
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:17,470
I’ll go on my own.

387
00:29:17,470 --> 00:29:18,430
Get on with your work.

388
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:45,710
Ye Qianyu.

389
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:49,000
It’s against personnel regulations

390
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:51,110
to ignore the General Manager.

391
00:29:54,950 --> 00:29:56,760
Morning, Mr. Shan.

392
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,190
Morning.

393
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:07,110
Mr. Shan, is there anything else?

394
00:30:09,070 --> 00:30:09,830
No.

395
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:11,920
I just want to inspect the rooms.

396
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,310
I’ll go to work.

397
00:31:02,350 --> 00:31:03,160
Mr. Shan,

398
00:31:03,710 --> 00:31:05,640
you don’t need to do that.

399
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:08,070
I can ask other cleaning staff to help.

400
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:11,280
As the General Manager,

401
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:13,080
it’s a plus to my image

402
00:31:13,420 --> 00:31:14,540
to show kindness occasionally.

403
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:15,320
Ah.

404
00:31:19,820 --> 00:31:22,170
Mr. Shan, I can do it. Leave it to me.

405
00:31:29,590 --> 00:31:30,470
Director Fan.

406
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:32,760
Dawei, where is Mr. Shan?

407
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:35,160
Mr. Shan went to Senwell Hotel
in the early morning

408
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,160
to supervise their work.

409
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:38,110
Why didn’t you go?

410
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:40,160
Mr. Shan said he wanted to go alone

411
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,400
and to enhance communication with employees.

412
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,140
What?

413
00:31:58,430 --> 00:32:00,590
Remember. Do it as early as possible…

414
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:01,920
Yunyi.

415
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,800
Mr. Shan,

416
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,230
don’t you have work to do?

417
00:32:20,470 --> 00:32:21,760
Or do you worry about my work

418
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:23,280
that you have to supervise in person?

419
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,000
I…

420
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,040
Come to inspect the rooms.

421
00:32:35,710 --> 00:32:37,680
Room inspection is a pivotal part

422
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,280
of the hotel management.

423
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,560
Because guests’ experience

424
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:43,680
determines the occupancy rate.

425
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:46,160
Senwell Hotel’s occupancy rate of this year

426
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:48,280
drops 20% compared with that of last year.

427
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:51,430
Despite of malicious competition,

428
00:32:51,830 --> 00:32:54,830
I wonder what the problem is.

429
00:32:57,590 --> 00:32:59,880
I don’t know anything about hotel management.

430
00:33:00,430 --> 00:33:02,070
But Tonghao told me once

431
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:04,920
that the secret of running a hotel
lies in details.

432
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:07,230
Senwell Hotel is lavish in decoration.

433
00:33:07,230 --> 00:33:09,310
But I think the smile on some employees’ faces

434
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,950
isn’t as bright as Fengqiao’s.

435
00:33:11,310 --> 00:33:13,160
The smell in the air is great,

436
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:15,800
but not as fragrant as flowers in Guanmei Inn.

437
00:33:15,950 --> 00:33:18,350
Towels in the room are soft,

438
00:33:18,520 --> 00:33:20,830
but they’re too plain and neat
that lose the warmth of home.

439
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:24,110
Good point.

440
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,430
Really?

441
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:29,210
It seems Tonghao is a great teacher.

442
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:31,900
Mr. Tonghao is brilliant.

443
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:33,710
Mr. Shan,

444
00:33:34,430 --> 00:33:36,710
why do you come today?

445
00:33:44,830 --> 00:33:47,000
I want to give you another chance to regret.

446
00:33:47,230 --> 00:33:48,070
What?

447
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:51,640
I think you must feel remorse yesterday

448
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:53,350
not to accept my feelings.

449
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:55,950
And as a girl,

450
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:57,520
you’re too shy to admit it.

451
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:59,880
So I’m right in front of you now

452
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,070
to give you another chance.

453
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,840
Cleaner on second floor!

454
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,280
Copy that.

455
00:34:10,720 --> 00:34:12,750
A guest spilt drinks on the stairs.

456
00:34:12,750 --> 00:34:14,200
Clean it up as soon as possible.

457
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:15,520
OK, copy that.

458
00:34:16,710 --> 00:34:17,520
Mr. Shan,

459
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:20,230
I’ll give you a minute to admire yourself.

460
00:34:20,910 --> 00:34:21,630
Bye-bye.

461
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:36,000
Ye Qianyu,

462
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:42,360
I never take back

463
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:43,800
what I said.

464
00:34:44,950 --> 00:34:46,230
And I won’t give up

465
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,230
on the decision I made.

466
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:05,290
This is your card key. Here.

467
00:35:31,080 --> 00:35:32,040
Director Fan.

468
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,120
Have you seen Mr. Shan?

469
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:36,150
Mr. Shan was here just now.

470
00:35:36,630 --> 00:35:38,360
He went downstairs with a colleague

471
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:39,360
of the Cleaning Department.

472
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:47,560
Joey.

473
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,120
Mr. Shan,

474
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:53,430
what’s up?

475
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:55,520
Someone fell off from the stairs
on the second floor.

476
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:56,560
Fell off?

477
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:01,660
Let’s go.

478
00:37:01,660 --> 00:37:02,420
All right.

479
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:21,420
= Operation Room =

480
00:37:40,390 --> 00:37:41,280
Go take a seat.

481
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:44,950
What’s up?

482
00:37:45,950 --> 00:37:46,800
Are you injured?

483
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:48,520
No, I’m fine.

484
00:37:55,080 --> 00:37:55,840
Junhao.

485
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,190
How is Yunyi?

486
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:00,840
Doctors are saving her.

487
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,430
What was going on?

488
00:38:02,870 --> 00:38:04,760
How could Yunyi fall off from the stairs

489
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:05,870
in the hotel?

490
00:38:08,430 --> 00:38:09,430
I’m sorry.

491
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:12,000
I was mopping the floor.

492
00:38:12,230 --> 00:38:13,470
It was slippery,

493
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:15,800
which led to Director Fan’s fall.

494
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,560
I’m sorry.

495
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:30,190
If anything happens to my daughter,

496
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:34,000
I will let you pay the price.

497
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,120
Mom,

498
00:38:40,470 --> 00:38:41,710
it’s just an accident.

499
00:38:41,710 --> 00:38:43,120
Don’t you see the situation here?

500
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:44,600
How could you speak for her?

501
00:38:50,230 --> 00:38:52,560
Mom, calm down.

502
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,320
Ye Qianyu,

503
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:00,950
Junhao and Yunyi is about to get married.

504
00:39:01,760 --> 00:39:03,150
I warn you.

505
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:05,870
Stay away from them!

506
00:39:07,390 --> 00:39:10,120
Don’t ever get in my sight!

507
00:39:11,190 --> 00:39:12,190
Get out!

508
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:16,430
I’m sorry.

509
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:23,710
- Yunyi! - Yunyi.

510
00:39:24,230 --> 00:39:25,230
- Yunyi. - Yunyi.

511
00:39:25,710 --> 00:39:28,120
Doctor, how is my daughter?

512
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:29,840
Her head was hit badly

513
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,840
which leads to coma

514
00:39:30,840 --> 00:39:33,040
and severe concussion.

515
00:39:33,230 --> 00:39:35,280
But these aren’t dangerous.

516
00:39:35,520 --> 00:39:36,520
What’s dangerous is

517
00:39:36,520 --> 00:39:38,120
that intracerebral hematoma is found

518
00:39:38,190 --> 00:39:40,430
and oppresses the optic nerve.

519
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:49,040
Yunyi.

520
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,000
Yunyi, you’re awake.

521
00:39:52,560 --> 00:39:53,560
Yunyi.

522
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:56,800
Yunyi.

523
00:39:57,150 --> 00:39:59,760
You’re awake. How do you feel?

524
00:40:00,040 --> 00:40:00,600
Mom.

525
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:01,710
I’m here.

526
00:40:01,710 --> 00:40:02,830
- Mom. - I’m here.

527
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,800
Mom is here.

528
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:08,000
My eyes.

529
00:40:08,390 --> 00:40:09,190
Eyes?

530
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,520
What’s wrong with them?

531
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:15,080
I can’t see anything.

532
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:21,840
Mom.

533
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:25,280
What…

534
00:40:25,710 --> 00:40:26,870
What’s going on?

535
00:40:26,870 --> 00:40:28,360
This is the consequence

536
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:30,230
when intracerebral hematoma
oppresses the optic nerve.

537
00:40:32,910 --> 00:40:33,870
Loss of vision.

538
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:37,910
Loss of vision?

539
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:41,080
Mom.

540
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:45,120
If the clot can dissolve itself,

541
00:40:45,120 --> 00:40:47,120
as the pressure on optic nerve is relieved,

542
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:48,910
she can regain her vision.

543
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,560
But if the clot stays,

544
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,040
we suggest

545
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:54,870
a surgery to remove it.

546
00:41:01,230 --> 00:41:02,390
It’s OK.

547
00:41:02,630 --> 00:41:03,520
What should I do?

548
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,120
You heard the doctor.

549
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,040
He said

550
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:07,430
it’s only temporary…

551
00:41:07,430 --> 00:41:08,600
Temporary loss of vision.

552
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:09,670
What should we do?

553
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,480
Cheer up. It’s OK.

554
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:12,990
- It’s OK. - Mom.

555
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:15,210
Yunyi.

556
00:41:16,810 --> 00:41:17,740
Mom.

557
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,000
Where is Junhao?

558
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,520
He’s here.

559
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:21,470
He’s here.

560
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:23,320
Junhao.

561
00:41:25,630 --> 00:41:26,600
Junhao.

562
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:32,430
You’ll be fine.

563
00:41:34,430 --> 00:41:35,430
Mom.

564
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:37,560
It’s gonna be fine.

565
00:41:38,910 --> 00:41:40,430
You’re OK.

566
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,600
Qianyu.

567
00:42:06,870 --> 00:42:08,040
Taichu.

568
00:42:10,230 --> 00:42:11,430
Is your hand OK?

569
00:42:12,840 --> 00:42:13,840
Yes.

570
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:15,600
Let me see.

571
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,430
It’s severe.

572
00:42:17,710 --> 00:42:18,520
Let me take you to the doctor.

573
00:42:18,750 --> 00:42:20,190
- I’m fine. - Let’s go.

574
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:23,320
Tell the hotel manager to fire Ye Qianyu.

575
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:25,230
Mom,

576
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:28,190
I told you it was an accident.

577
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:29,600
I don’t care if it was an accident or not,

578
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:31,600
I don’t want to see her again.

579
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,390
I won’t fire her.

580
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:42,760
What’s wrong with you now?

581
00:42:43,470 --> 00:42:44,840
You weren’t like this before.

582
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,230
You were obedient.

583
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:48,470
Now you go against my will more than once

584
00:42:48,470 --> 00:42:50,190
for that girl.

585
00:42:50,360 --> 00:42:52,520
Is Ye Qianyu more important than Yunyi

586
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:54,080
or the company?

587
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:57,360
You…

588
00:43:02,950 --> 00:43:03,760
Junhao.

589
00:43:09,870 --> 00:43:11,080
Is Ye Qianyu

590
00:43:12,950 --> 00:43:15,190
more important than Yunyi in your eyes?

591
00:43:32,190 --> 00:43:33,760
Qianyu, are you alright?

592
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:38,840
Now you remember to care about Qianyu.

593
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:40,080
Don’t you think it’s too late?

594
00:43:42,870 --> 00:43:44,800
Taichu, we should go.

595
00:43:49,080 --> 00:43:49,870
Qianyu…

596
00:43:51,150 --> 00:43:52,670
If you can’t take care of Yunyi,

597
00:43:53,760 --> 00:43:55,160
please let her go.

598
00:44:18,080 --> 00:44:18,800
Thank you.

599
00:44:21,600 --> 00:44:22,430
Qianyu,

600
00:44:23,120 --> 00:44:24,630
stay in my home for a few days.

601
00:44:25,040 --> 00:44:27,430
Or Mama Jinzhi would be worried

602
00:44:27,430 --> 00:44:28,520
if she found you injured.

603
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:30,710
I’ve called her.

604
00:44:31,670 --> 00:44:32,910
Thank you, Taichu.

605
00:44:54,320 --> 00:44:55,360
What’s this?

606
00:44:55,520 --> 00:44:56,320
For you.

607
00:44:58,280 --> 00:44:59,080
Thank you.

608
00:45:06,390 --> 00:45:08,910
Put behind what you should let go.

609
00:45:10,040 --> 00:45:10,910
Qianyu,

610
00:45:11,190 --> 00:45:12,600
have you ever considered

611
00:45:12,840 --> 00:45:14,800
to travel around the world with me?

612
00:45:48,080 --> 00:45:53,100
♪ Distance between us ♪

613
00:45:56,400 --> 00:46:01,490
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

614
00:46:02,550 --> 00:46:06,530
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

615
00:46:06,550 --> 00:46:10,240
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

616
00:46:10,790 --> 00:46:18,190
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

617
00:46:19,430 --> 00:46:23,730
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

618
00:46:23,750 --> 00:46:27,510
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

619
00:46:27,750 --> 00:46:31,990
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

620
00:46:32,010 --> 00:46:35,520
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

621
00:46:36,030 --> 00:46:40,190
♪ You painted my life ♪

622
00:46:40,210 --> 00:46:43,790
♪ With flowers ♪

623
00:46:43,810 --> 00:46:47,750
♪ You raised me up ♪

624
00:46:47,770 --> 00:46:51,170
♪ From that moment on ♪

625
00:46:51,700 --> 00:46:54,460
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪
